-- Variable names

x1,x2...  : similar variables in the same context

c         : char
i,j       : indexing integers
o         : offset
n, m      : size integers
k         : other integers

s, t      : string (t is used more for a mutable, temporary value)
pre       : prefix
suf       : suffix

l         : label

e         : edge
c         : child
s         : sibling
p         : parent
scan      : scanner

m         : matching

st        : suffix tree
-- Style

Two spaces between functions in c files
One space between functions in h files
